<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: beautiful aurora -->
  <Aurora.stages.beautiful_aurora.label>美麗極光</Aurora.stages.beautiful_aurora.label>
  <!-- EN: The view is amazing. -->
  <Aurora.stages.beautiful_aurora.description>這景色真美妙。</Aurora.stages.beautiful_aurora.description>
  
  <!-- EN: colonist left unburied -->
  <ColonistLeftUnburied.stages.colonist_left_unburied.label>有殖民者未安葬</ColonistLeftUnburied.stages.colonist_left_unburied.label>
  <!-- EN: One of us died and we're just leaving them lying in the open. Nobody should be left like that. People deserve a decent burial. -->
  <ColonistLeftUnburied.stages.colonist_left_unburied.description>我們有同伴死了，我們卻讓他們曝屍荒野。沒有人希望受到這種待遇。死者們應該要有一個安葬。</ColonistLeftUnburied.stages.colonist_left_unburied.description>
  
  <!-- EN: minor passion for my work -->
  <DoingPassionateWork.stages.minor_passion_for_my_work.label>對我的工作有點熱情</DoingPassionateWork.stages.minor_passion_for_my_work.label>
  <!-- EN: I enjoy my work. -->
  <DoingPassionateWork.stages.minor_passion_for_my_work.description>我享受我的工作。</DoingPassionateWork.stages.minor_passion_for_my_work.description>
  <!-- EN: burning passion for my work -->
  <DoingPassionateWork.stages.burning_passion_for_my_work.label>對我的工作充滿熱情</DoingPassionateWork.stages.burning_passion_for_my_work.label>
  <!-- EN: I love my work. I could do this all day, every day. -->
  <DoingPassionateWork.stages.burning_passion_for_my_work.description>我熱愛我的工作，我可以每天做整天。</DoingPassionateWork.stages.burning_passion_for_my_work.description>
  
  <!-- EN: joywire -->
  <Joywire.stages.joywire.label>樂絲晶片</Joywire.stages.joywire.label>
  <!-- EN: It feels amazing. -->
  <Joywire.stages.joywire.description>這感覺真美妙。</Joywire.stages.joywire.description>
  
  <!-- EN: missing tongue -->
  <MissingTongue.stages.missing_tongue.label>失去舌頭</MissingTongue.stages.missing_tongue.label>
  <!-- EN: I am missing my tongue. It is so frustrating not being able to speak! -->
  <MissingTongue.stages.missing_tongue.description>我很想念我的舌頭。不能說話實在太鬱悶了！</MissingTongue.stages.missing_tongue.description>
  
  <!-- EN: naked -->
  <Naked.stages.naked.label>一絲不掛</Naked.stages.naked.label>
  <!-- EN: I'm naked. This is humiliating. -->
  <Naked.stages.naked.description>我全身赤裸。好丟臉。</Naked.stages.naked.description>
  
  <!-- EN: minor pain -->
  <Pain.stages.minor_pain.label>小痛</Pain.stages.minor_pain.label>
  <!-- EN: Ow... That hurts. -->
  <Pain.stages.minor_pain.description>唉呦...好痛。</Pain.stages.minor_pain.description>
  <!-- EN: serious pain -->
  <Pain.stages.serious_pain.label>疼痛</Pain.stages.serious_pain.label>
  <!-- EN: Ughhh... When will it end? -->
  <Pain.stages.serious_pain.description>啊...痛苦什麼時候結束？</Pain.stages.serious_pain.description>
  <!-- EN: intense pain -->
  <Pain.stages.intense_pain.label>痛不欲生</Pain.stages.intense_pain.label>
  <!-- EN: Make it stop... make it stop... make it stop... -->
  <Pain.stages.intense_pain.description>停下來...停下來...停下來...</Pain.stages.intense_pain.description>
  <!-- EN: mind-shattering pain -->
  <Pain.stages.mindshattering_pain.label>極痛入骨</Pain.stages.mindshattering_pain.label>
  <!-- EN: AAAAAHHH! -->
  <Pain.stages.mindshattering_pain.description>啊啊啊！</Pain.stages.mindshattering_pain.description>
  
  <!-- EN: psychic soothe -->
  <PsychicDrone.stages.psychic_soothe.label>心靈安撫</PsychicDrone.stages.psychic_soothe.label>
  <!-- EN: It's like a calming voice at the back of my mind, soothing me, settling my nerves. -->
  <PsychicDrone.stages.psychic_soothe.description>腦海中好像有個溫柔的迴音，安撫我，消除我的緊張。</PsychicDrone.stages.psychic_soothe.description>
  <!-- EN: low psychic drone -->
  <PsychicDrone.stages.low_psychic_drone.label>低心靈干擾</PsychicDrone.stages.low_psychic_drone.label>
  <!-- EN: It's like a scratching at the back of my mind. A voice, whispering. I can only make out a few words, and I don't like them. -->
  <PsychicDrone.stages.low_psychic_drone.description>腦海中有個竊竊私語的迴音揮之不去。我只能聽懂幾個詞，我不喜歡這些聲音。</PsychicDrone.stages.low_psychic_drone.description>
  <!-- EN: moderate psychic drone -->
  <PsychicDrone.stages.moderate_psychic_drone.label>中心靈干擾</PsychicDrone.stages.moderate_psychic_drone.label>
  <!-- EN: I feel like someone is always just out of sight, speaking to me. The voice changes but the message doesn't. I'm supposed to hurt people. Make it go away! -->
  <PsychicDrone.stages.moderate_psychic_drone.description>我感覺有個看不見的東西在對我說話。迴音會變，但内容始终相同。我應該要傷害别人。讓這聲音消失！</PsychicDrone.stages.moderate_psychic_drone.description>
  <!-- EN: high psychic drone -->
  <PsychicDrone.stages.high_psychic_drone.label>高心靈干擾</PsychicDrone.stages.high_psychic_drone.label>
  <!-- EN: The voice is unbearably loud. It's hard to concentrate. I find myself talking back to it, yelling at it. But it just keeps shouting! -->
  <PsychicDrone.stages.high_psychic_drone.description>迴音大到無法忍受。注意力難以集中。我發現我會不自覺對這迴音大吼。只是迴音還是一樣大聲！</PsychicDrone.stages.high_psychic_drone.description>
  <!-- EN: extreme psychic drone -->
  <PsychicDrone.stages.extreme_psychic_drone.label>超級心靈干擾</PsychicDrone.stages.extreme_psychic_drone.label>
  <!-- EN: My heart pounds and I'm sweating. All I can think of is hurting and suffering and all these enemies around me. They're my nightmare, my nightmare, my nightmare... -->
  <PsychicDrone.stages.extreme_psychic_drone.description>我的心臟不停地跳動、汗不停地流。我能想到的只有傷害、痛苦、十面埋伏的敵人。它們是我的惡夢，我的惡夢，我的惡夢...</PsychicDrone.stages.extreme_psychic_drone.description>
  
  <!-- EN: psychic emanator soothe -->
  <PsychicEmanatorSoothe.stages.psychic_emanator_soothe.label>心靈安撫散發器</PsychicEmanatorSoothe.stages.psychic_emanator_soothe.label>
  <!-- EN: The psychic emanator makes me feel strange, but also very relaxed. -->
  <PsychicEmanatorSoothe.stages.psychic_emanator_soothe.description>心靈安撫散發器讓我感到奇怪，但也很放鬆。</PsychicEmanatorSoothe.stages.psychic_emanator_soothe.description>
  
  <!-- UNUSED -->
  <PsychicEntropyHangover.stages.psychic_hangover.label>心靈宿醉</PsychicEntropyHangover.stages.psychic_hangover.label>
  <PsychicEntropyHangover.stages.psychic_hangover.description>我的眼睛痠痛，渾身無力，但我知道這是來自於我的大腦。</PsychicEntropyHangover.stages.psychic_hangover.description>
  
  <!-- EN: rot stink -->
  <RotStink.stages.rot_stink.label>腐爛臭氣</RotStink.stages.rot_stink.label>
  <!-- EN: A rotten stink invades my nostrils and sticks to my skin. It makes me sick. -->
  <RotStink.stages.rot_stink.description>腐爛臭氣侵入我的鼻子，而且纏著我的皮膚揮之不去。我覺得很不舒服。</RotStink.stages.rot_stink.description>
  <!-- EN: awful rot stink -->
  <RotStink.stages.awful_rot_stink.label>嚴重腐爛臭氣</RotStink.stages.awful_rot_stink.label>
  <!-- EN: The stench of rot is so thick I almost feel like I'm swimming in it. I can hardly breathe in this filth! -->
  <RotStink.stages.awful_rot_stink.description>腐爛物的惡臭濃厚得令我幾乎能在裡面游起來了。我不能在這垃圾堆中呼吸！</RotStink.stages.awful_rot_stink.description>
  
  <!-- EN: rot stink lingering -->
  <RotStinkLingering.stages.rot_stink_lingering.label>腐爛臭氣纏身</RotStinkLingering.stages.rot_stink_lingering.label>
  <!-- EN: That rot stink was horrible - and it feels like it's still stuck to me. -->
  <RotStinkLingering.stages.rot_stink_lingering.description>那腐爛臭氣實在太可怕了——我現在仍覺得那臭氣還在纏著我。</RotStinkLingering.stages.rot_stink_lingering.description>
  
  <!-- EN: sharing bed -->
  <SharedBed.stages.sharing_bed.label>共用床鋪</SharedBed.stages.sharing_bed.label>
  <!-- EN: I have to share a bed with someone who I don't particularly want to. -->
  <SharedBed.stages.sharing_bed.description>我得和一個我不願同床的人一起睡。</SharedBed.stages.sharing_bed.description>
  
  <!-- EN: toxic fallout -->
  <ToxicFallout.stages.toxic_fallout.label>毒霧霾</ToxicFallout.stages.toxic_fallout.label>
  <!-- EN: Sickly yellow toxic flakes drift around me like snow. The air burns my skin, throat, and lungs everywhere it touches. -->
  <ToxicFallout.stages.toxic_fallout.description>糟糕的黃色有毒飛屑有如雪花般在我身邊飄盪。我的皮膚、喉嚨和肺部，這些空氣所到之處都感到灼痛。</ToxicFallout.stages.toxic_fallout.description>
  
</LanguageData>